    <item>
      <title>克拉伦斯·托马斯乘坐哈兰·克罗的私人飞机进行了更多旅行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/clarence-thomas-took-more-trips-on-harlan-crow-s-private-jet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据参议院民主党公布的文件，美国最高法院大法官克拉伦斯·托马斯未能披露由共和党巨额捐款人哈兰·克罗支付的至少三次美国私人飞机旅行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/clarence-thomas-took-more-trips-on-harlan-crow-s-private-jet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登誓言盟友将与乌克兰站在一起“直到他们获胜”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/biden-vows-allies-will-stand-with-ukraine-until-they-prevail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登对一项新的安全协议、向乌克兰提供 500 亿美元援助的计划以及扩大针对莫斯科的制裁表示赞赏，认为这向俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京发出了明确信号，即美国及其盟友不会“放弃”对基辅的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/biden-vows-allies-will-stand-with-ukraine-until-they-prevail</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 19:51:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普告诉首席执行官他将把企业税率降至 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/trump-tells-ceos-he-would-cut-corporate-tax-rate-to-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普承诺将企业税率降至 20%，进一步降低他在任总统期间已大幅削减的美国最大企业所得税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/trump-tells-ceos-he-would-cut-corporate-tax-rate-to-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 19:51:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国左翼团结起来挑战马克龙和勒庞的权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/france-s-left-unites-to-challenge-le-pen-macron-for-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国左翼政党结成联盟，在即将举行的立法选举中齐心协力，民意调查显示，该联盟有望赢得仅次于玛丽娜·勒庞的国民联盟的第二大党团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/france-s-left-unites-to-challenge-le-pen-macron-for-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 18:46:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大总理 Poilievre 当选后将重新考虑上调资本利得税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/canada-s-poilievre-to-review-capital-gains-tax-hike-if-elected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 承诺，如果当选总理，将重新审查资本利得税上调措施，但他不会承诺废除该措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/canada-s-poilievre-to-review-capital-gains-tax-hike-if-elected</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 18:38:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关键选举迫在眉睫，南非新政府尚未达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/anc-says-south-african-parties-still-discussing-unity-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距总统西里尔·拉马福萨竞选连任国家元首仅剩几个小时，南非各政党仍在继续就组建新政府进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/anc-says-south-african-parties-still-discussing-unity-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 18:03:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼与马斯克在乌克兰的 Starlink 计划的协议延长六个月，金额达 1400 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/pentagon-extends-deal-with-musk-s-starlink-in-ukraine-for-six-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼与埃隆·马斯克的 SpaceX 续签了为期六个月的合同，为乌克兰提供 Starlink 互联网服务，这一新迹象表明双方已摆脱了在冲突地区如何使用终端的争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/pentagon-extends-deal-with-musk-s-starlink-in-ukraine-for-six-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 15:56:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>也门附近船只在几天内遭遇第二次袭击后起火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/ship-on-fire-near-yemen-after-second-attack-in-as-many-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘小型货船在亚丁湾航行时被三枚射弹击中并起火，这是两天内发生的第二起重大事件，也是新一轮袭击事件的升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/ship-on-fire-near-yemen-after-second-attack-in-as-many-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 12:28:21 GMT</pubDate>
